Be aware that this torrent is stuck at 99.74% with no likelyhood that there's anyone out there with the remaining 0.26%.....

And no, it doesn't install!  Boo.

Some good news for the 200+ (currently) people stuck on 99.74%.  Fortunately, the missing download (that 0.26%) is a single file not stored in the main compressed archive, and simply creating a 'dummy-file' prior to running the 'Setup.exe' installer will result in a successful installation.

So, in the "Adobe" folder where the rest of the files reside, create a file called "ReadMe.html" (with Notepad for example).  Now run 'Setup.exe' and all should be well!
